<TEXT>     The chemical spill has closed off 10 miles of Highway 101 near the
ocean-front community of Seacliff, between San Barbara and Los Angeles, with
detours taking travelers up to four hours, authorities said. Authorities now
say it will be sometime Thursday before the key north-south route reopens.;
