   Senate Supporters of Fuel Economy Bill
   Lose Vote, Dooming Measure This Year
   ----
   By Rose Gutfeld
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/26/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
</SO>
<CO>
   JAPAN TOYOY J.SUZ HMC G.VOW J.DHM
</CO>
<IN>
