   Ford Motor Offers
   Incentive Financing
   On Escorts, Tracers
</HL>
<DATE>
08/21/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
<CO>
   F
</CO>
<IN>
